## Description {#details}

A tuple of MDNodes.

Despite its name, a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/namedmdnode">NamedMDNode</a> isn&#39;t itself an <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mdnode">MDNode</a>.

NamedMDNodes are named module-level entities that contain lists of MDNodes.

It is illegal for a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/namedmdnode">NamedMDNode</a> to appear as an operand of an <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mdnode">MDNode</a>.

Definition at line 1737 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/ir/metadata-h">Metadata.h</a>.
